Interface Buildable<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The Class for Construct
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Contact.Builder, Education.Builder, Experience.Builder, Locale.Builder, Skill.Builder, Subscriber.Builder, User.Builder

    public interface Buildable<T>
    Markup Interface for Buildable Objects
    Builders Must Have:
    • Empty Default Constructor with Private Accessor
    • Contains Same Fields of Implementation Class
    • Constructor with Required Fields
    • All Setter Fields Must Return {this} or Current Builder
    Since:
    1.0
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    felipe
